                <div class=\"c-box normal fade\">\n                  <h5>1日の勤務時間</h5>\n                  <pict><img src=\"../img/recruit/img_data_time.svg\" alt=\"1日の勤務時間　7時間15分　9:00→17:30　時差出勤OK 休憩60分＋おやつ休憩15分\"/></pict>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"c-box normal fade\">\n                  <h5>有給消化率</h5>\n                  <pict><img src=\"../img/recruit/img_data_yukyu.svg\" alt=\"有給消化率　70%\"/></pict>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"c-box normal fade\">\n                  <h5>平均勤続年数</h5>\n                  <pict><img src=\"../img/recruit/img_data_kinzoku.svg\" alt=\"平均勤続年数　12年\"/></pict>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"c-box normal fade\">\n                  <h5>育休取得後の復帰率</h5>\n                  <pict><img src=\"../img/recruit/img_data_ikukyu.svg\" alt=\"育休取得後の復帰率　100%\"/></pict>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"sec__inner\" id=\"employee\">\n              <h3 class=\"ttl-clmn fade\">社員について</h3>\n              <div class=\"inset__fx__sb-wp c-data__clmn\">\n                <div class=\"c-box normal fade\">\n                  <h5>男女比</h5>\n                  <pict><img src=\"../img/recruit/img_data_gender.svg\" alt=\"男女比　男性51%　女性49%\"/></pict>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"c-box normal fade\">\n                  <h5>新卒・キャリア</h5>\n                  <pict><img src=\"../img/recruit/img_data_career.svg\" alt=\"新卒・キャリア　新卒25%　キャリア75%\"/></pict>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"c-box normal fade\">\n                  <h5>新卒文系・理系</h5>\n                  <pict><img src=\"../img/recruit/img_data_hands.svg\" alt=\"新卒文系・理系　文系50%　　理系50%\"/></pict>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"sec__inner\" id=\"basis\">\n              <h3 class=\"ttl-clmn fade\">基本情報</h3>\n              <div class=\"inset__fx__sb-wp c-data__clmn\">\n                <div class=\"c-box 